Program for visualizing SRTM height maps using C++/OpenGL/GLUT

Author: Michal Karpinski


How to use:

1. Go to ./src/
2. Type: make all
3. Type: ./prog.e <path to hgt file>

Controls:

Left/Right arrow keys: rotate camera horizontaly
PageUp/PageDown arrow keys: move camera up/down
Up/Down arrow keys: move camera front/back
F1: change view (spectator horizontal view / eagle eye view)
Esc: exit program
